answersResultList.title: Mostly Capricorn.
answersResultList.resultContent: Sometimes you take things a little too far. You're not mean, just easily blinded by the thrill of the chase or the rush of victory. At least you surround yourself with people whose skin is as thick as yours. You take a rational, systematic approach to problems that might launch others into a panic. Like a true Capricorn, you're good at managing time and money, and while your loyalty occasionally wavers, you're satisfied to do right by the people who do right by you. If you rush into relationships sometimes, it's only because you're always ready for a happy ending.

answersResultList.title: Somewhat Capricorn.
answersResultList.resultContent: You can be serious if the situation requires it, but you'll also do whatever it takes to start a wave of giggling. You understand and appreciate moderation, which is somewhat Capricorn of you, but you don't always practice what you preach, especially when excess appeals to you. Yes, you pay the piper for this, and that worries you a lot when the bill comes due, but the lesson fades away when you recover from the sore body, broken heart, hangover, or financial downturn. You certainly know how to repair any damage you inflict. If this cycle bothers you, there's hope.

You can afford to be generous -- there's always room in the budget to shower gifts and treats on those who deserve them.
